*  109 - *var FENCE: seal must block when tail anchor fails
*  This is the canonical beauty.sno bug. Was crash on csnobol4.
        cmd = FENCE('a' | 'ab')
        s = 'ab'
        s  POS(0) *cmd RPOS(0)                                :S(BAD)F(GOOD)
BAD     OUTPUT = 'should not reach (alt was tried)'           :(END)
GOOD    OUTPUT = 'sealed via star-var'
END
